Revision history for Perl-Tokenizer

0.03    2015-09-04
        - Added support for the new bitwise operators (`^.`, `&.` and `|.`)

0.02    2015-07-23
        - Fixed the parsing of '__DATA__' when it's followed by a fat comma.

0.01    2015-07-16
        - First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
